data.description: This 4/3.5 has freshly painted hardy plank (04/20), wrap around porch. Walkout master BR to private corner. Walk-in closet, jacuzzi tub & stand up shower, jack & jill upstairs and a full bath with 4th bedroom.  New roof 01/21. Partially floored attic (3 accesses), window seats w/storage, office/game room/bedroom, formal DR, Plum & peach trees, blueberry & blackberry bushes.Common area w/ pond and walking path.  Zoned for Dothan City or Dale Co Schools. Rose bushes on side do not remain.
